#. module: energy_communities_cooperator
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_communities_cooperator.email_template_confirmation_voluntary_share
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"                        Dear <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t>,<br><br>\n"
"                        We confirm that we have correctly received your request to make a voluntary contribution to the capital social of <b><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></b>, with the following data:<br><br>\n"
"                        <ul>\n"
"                            <li>Partner VAT: <b><t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t></b></li>\n"
"                            <li>Partner name: <b><t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t> <t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t></b></li>\n"
"                            <li>Charging account finished on: <b><t t-out=\"object.iban[-4:]\"></t></b></li>\n"
"                            <li>Subscription amount: <b><t t-out=\"object.subscription_amount\"></t> €</b></li>\n"
"                        </ul>\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        In the next few days you will receive the bank charge in this account, please verify that all the data\n"
"                        provided is correct and you have the money you want to invest, to avoid any incident in the\n"
"                        draft of the receipt.\n"
"                        <br><br>\n"
"                        Once the validity of the payment has been verified, you will receive a new notification confirming the contribution made.\n"
"                        <br><br>\n"
"                        Thank you for your involvement and we inform you that for any doubt or clarification you can\n"
"                        <t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\">\n"
"                        consult our website: <a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a>\n"
"                        or\n"
"                        </t> send us an email to <t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t>.\n"
"                        <br><br>\n"
"                        Get the word out by explaining the project to family and friends. The more we are, the further we will go!\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        Thank you very much and good energy!\n"
"                        <br><br>\n"
"                        We keep in touch for any questions.<br>\n"
"                        Yours faithfully,<br>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">Maitea<t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t> ,<br><br> Gizarte-kapitalera borondatezko ekarpena egiteko zure eskaera behar bezala jaso dugula baieztatzen dugu.<b><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></b> , datu hauekin:<br><br><ul><li> Bazkidearen BEZa:<b><t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t></b></li><li> Bazkidearen izena:<b><t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t><t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t></b></li><li> Kontua kargatzen amaitu da:<b><t t-out=\"object.iban[-4:]\"></t></b></li><li> Harpidetza zenbatekoa: <b><t t-out=\"object.subscription_amount\"></t>€</b></li></ul><br> Hurrengo egunetan bankuko kargua jasoko duzu kontu honetan, mesedez egiaztatu emandako datu guztiak zuzenak direla eta inbertitu nahi duzun dirua duzula, ordainagiriaren zirriborroan gorabeherarik ekiditeko.<br><br> Ordainketaren baliozkotasuna egiaztatu ondoren, egindako ekarpena berresten duen jakinarazpen berri bat jasoko duzu.<br><br> Eskerrik asko zuen parte-hartzeagatik eta jakinarazten dizuegu edozein zalantza edo argibide izanez gero,<t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\"> kontsultatu gure webgunea:<a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a> edo</t> bidali mezu elektroniko bat helbide honetara<t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t> .<br><br> Zabaldu berria proiektua familiari eta lagunei azalduz. Zenbat eta gehiago izan, orduan eta urrunago iritsiko gara!<br> Mila esker eta energia ona!<br><br> Edozein zalantza argitzeko harremanetan jarraitzen dugu.<br> Zurekin adeitasunez,<br></p></div>\n"
"            "

#. module: energy_communities_cooperator
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_communities_cooperator.email_template_conditions_voluntary_share
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"                    Hello <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>,<br><br>\n"
"                    Recently we have allready charged your account the amount corresponding to your voluntary contribution to the share capital of <b><t t-out=\"object.company_id.comercial_name or object.company_id.name\"></t></b>.<br><br>\n"
"                    We take this opportunity to <b>thank you</b>, once again, for your involvement with the objective to promote actions and projects that contribute to an energy and social transition.<br><br>\n"
"                    Please find in attachment your <t t-out=\"object.company_id.comercial_name or object.company_id.name\"></t> cooperator certificate.<br><br>\n"
"                    Get the word out by explaining the project to family and friends. The more we are, the further we will go!<br><br>\n"
"                    We keep in touch for any questions.<br><br>\n"
"                    Yours faithfully,<br>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">Kaixo<t t-out=\"object.name\"></t> ,<br><br> Duela gutxi, zure kontuan kargatu dugu zure kapital sozialean egindako borondatezko ekarpenari dagokion zenbatekoa.<b><t t-out=\"object.company_id.comercial_name or object.company_id.name\"></t></b> .<br><br> Aukera hau baliatzen dugu berriro ere <b>eskerrak emateko</b> energia eta gizarte trantsizioan laguntzen duten ekintzak eta proiektuak sustatzeko helburuarekin egindako inplikazioagatik.<br><br> Mesedez, erantsian aurkituko duzu zure<t t-out=\"object.company_id.comercial_name or object.company_id.name\"></t> lankidetza-ziurtagiria.<br><br> Zabaldu berria proiektua familiari eta lagunei azalduz. Zenbat eta gehiago izan, orduan eta urrunago iritsiko gara!<br><br> Edozein zalantza argitzeko harremanetan jarraitzen dugu.<br><br> Zurekin adeitasunez,<br></p></div>\n"
"            "

#. module: energy_communities_cooperator
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_communities_cooperator.email_template_voluntary_share_interest_return
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"                    Hello <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.firstname\"></t>,<br><br>\n"
"                    We have generated the yearly interest return of your voluntary shares contribution.<br>\n"
"                    <t t-if=\"object.partner_bank_id.acc_number\">\n"
"                    Soon you'll receive a transfer on your IBAN account finished on: <t t-out=\"object.partner_bank_id.acc_number[-4:]\"></t><br><br>.\n"
"                    </t>\n"
"                    <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"                    Soon you'll receive a transfer on your IBAN account.<br><br>\n"
"                    </t>\n"
"                    The summary of the transaction:<br>\n"
"                    <ul>\n"
"                        <t t-if=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id\">\n"
"                            <li><strong>Period:</strong> from <t t-out=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id.start_date_period.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')\"></t> to <t t-out=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id.end_date_period.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')\"></t></li>\n"
"                        </t>\n"
"                        <li><strong>Total contribution:</strong> <t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.voluntary_share_total_contribution).replace('.',',')\"></t>€</li>\n"
"                        <li><strong>Total interest:</strong> <t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_untaxed).replace('.',',')\"></t>€</li>\n"
"                        <li><strong>Taxes:</strong> <t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_tax).replace('.',',')\"></t>€</li>\n"
"                        <li><strong>Total to receive:</strong> <t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_total).replace('.',',')\"></t>€</li>\n"
"                    </ul>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Don't hesitate to contact us at <a t-if=\"object.company_id.email\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.email\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t></a> for any question you might have using the code: <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t><br>\n"
"                    Thanks for your contribution helping generate our green energy.<br><br>\n"
"                    Yours faithfully,<br>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">Kaixo<t t-out=\"object.partner_id.firstname\"></t> ,<br><br> Zure borondatezko akzioen ekarpenaren urteko interes-itzulera sortu dugu.<br><t t-if=\"object.partner_bank_id.acc_number\"> Laster zure IBAN kontuan transferentzia bat jasoko duzu, honako datarekin amaituta:<t t-out=\"object.partner_bank_id.acc_number[-4:]\"></t><br><br> .</t><t t-else=\"\"> Laster transferentzia bat jasoko duzu zure IBAN kontuan.<br><br></t> Transakzioaren laburpena:<br><ul><t t-if=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id\"><li> <strong>Aldia:</strong> -tik<t t-out=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id.start_date_period.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')\"></t> ra<t t-out=\"object.voluntary_share_interest_return_id.end_date_period.strftime('%d/%m/%Y')\"></t></li></t><li> <strong>Ekarpen osoa:</strong><t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.voluntary_share_total_contribution).replace('.',',')\"></t> €</li><li> <strong>Interes totala:</strong><t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_untaxed).replace('.',',')\"></t> €</li><li> <strong>Zergak:</strong><t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_tax).replace('.',',')\"></t> €</li><li> <strong>Jasotzeko guztira:</strong><t t-out=\"('%.2f'% object.amount_total).replace('.',',')\"></t> €</li></ul><br> Ez izan zalantzarik gurekin harremanetan jartzeko helbidean.<a t-if=\"object.company_id.email\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.email\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t></a> Kodea erabiliz edozein zalantza izanez gero:<t t-out=\"object.name\"></t><br> Eskerrik asko gure energia berdea sortzen laguntzeko zure ekarpenagatik.<br><br> Zurekin adeitasunez,<br></p></div>\n"
"            "

